<div class='email-signature-creator page'><div class="container-fluid">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-4 col-md-offset-1">
      <h4>1. Fill out your info.</h4>

      <form>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="personName">Name</label>
          {{input type="text" class="form-control" value=name id='personName'  placeholder="Your Name"}}
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="position">Position</label>
          {{input type="text" class="form-control" id="position" value=position placeholder="Position"}}
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="phone">Phone Number</label>
          {{input type="text" class="form-control" id="phone" value=phone placeholder="410-XXX-XXXX"}}
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-6 col-md-offset-1">
      <div class='preview'>
        <h4>2. Drag-select the signature with your mouse, then copy it.</h4>
        <hr />
        <table border="0" style="text-align:left;font-family:Lato,Arial,sans-serif;color:rgb(74,74,74);font-size:14px;line-height:18px">
            <tr>
                <td style="vertical-align:top"></td>
                <td class="text dash" style="vertical-align:top;padding-left:14px;color:rgb(170,170,170);text-align:left">
                    &mdash;
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <a href="http://www.allovue.com" alt="Visit Allovue.com"><img src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/allovue-design/assets/allovue-logo.png"></a>
                </td>
                <td class="text" style="padding-left:14px">
                    <h4 style="margin:0;padding:0;font-weight:bold;font-size:15px;">{{#if name}}{{name}}{{else}}Your Name{{/if}}</h4>
                    <p style="margin:0;padding:0">{{#if position}}{{position}}{{else}}Position{{/if}}</p>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td></td>
                <td class="text phone" style=
                "padding-top:10px;color:rgb(170,170,170);padding-left:14px">
                    <p style="margin:0;padding:0"><a href="http://www.allovue.com" alt="Visit Allovue.com" style="color:rgb(170,170,170);text-decoration:none;">Allovue</a></p>
                    <p style="margin:0;padding:0"><a href="tel:{{phone}}" style="color:rgb(170,170,170);text-decoration:none;">{{#if phone}}{{phone}}{{else}}410-XXX-XXXX{{/if}}</a></p>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
        <hr />
      </div>
      <h4>3. Paste in to your email client's signature area.</h4>
      <h5>For example in Gmail, select settings:</h5>
        <img src='assets/gmail-settings-dropdown.png'/>
      <h5>Scroll to the signature area and paste it in. Be careful not to paste it into the autoresponder section. Also Check the "Insert this signature..." box.</h5>
        <img src='assets/gmail-signature-pasted.png'/>

      <h5>Save your changes</h5>
      <img src='assets/gmail-save-button.png'/>

      <hr />

      {{!-- Putting this here for future reference
            http://www.htmlescape.net/htmlescape_tool.html - Only had `Replace < > "` checked
